 described by a power-law with a single break. The derived\nlimits can be interpreted in the context of many possible source classes. In\norder to enhance the flexibility of the results, we publish the full posterior\nfrom our analysis, which can be used to establish limits on specific population\nmodels that would contribute to the observed IceCube neutrino flux.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Sep 2019 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-14"}
