ately predict the\nNLI power. This difference could be up to 4.3 dB for a 10.011 THz system with\n1001 channels at 10 Gbaud.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Sep 2019 21:27:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Jun 2020 16:27:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Dec 2020 11:36:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-04"}
