 phoenix\" scenario, no DSA of the fossil electron population is\nrequired to account for the observed brightening and flattening of the spectra,\nadiabatic compression effects are sufficient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Sep 2019 21:52:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
