|\\cdot \\|$ circle. We prove that for $n \\geq 7$, every\nline-like crescent configuration of size $n$ in the Chebyshev norm must have a\nrigid structure. Specifically, it must be a perpendicular perturbation of\nequally spaced points on a horizontal or vertical line.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2019 01:44:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Nov 2019 14:32:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-20"}
